
Build for QNX
=============
* Make sure CMake 3.5 or newer is installed
* Install QNX7.0 SDK
* Initialize submodules:
  - git submodule init
  - git submodule update

* For build dependencies
  # cd qnx_port
  #./build_deps.sh

* For build libxl4bus
  # cd qnx_port
  #./build_lib.sh

* For deploy on target we need these binaries

    - xl4bus-broker     |
    - libxl4bus.so      | => Generated when build libxl4bus
    - libjansson.so.4   |

	- libsocket.so.3    |
	- libcares.so.1     |
	- libm.so.3         |
	- libcrypto.so.2    | => Included in QNX7 SDK
	- libc.so.4         |
	- libssl.so.2       |
	- libz.so.2         |
